content.rendered:
World Youth Games – Montenegro: ANABA Team Announcement

ANABA is excited to announce that we are sending a talented team to represent Australia at the prestigious World Youth Games in Budva, Montenegro! This incredible opportunity allows our young boxers to showcase their skills on an international stage, competing against the world’s best. Our team is ready to bring their hard work and determination to the ring, and we couldn’t be prouder. Stay tuned for updates on their journey and support Team Australia as they make their mark in Montenegro! #TeamAustralia #ANABA #WorldYouthGames #Montenegro2024
